# Scheduling & receivers

- Primary scheduling lives in `BackupJobs` + `SmsBackupWorker` via **WorkManager** (unique OneTimeWork + ContentUriTrigger).
- Runtime registration for SMS/MMS/`com.zegoggles.smssync.BACKUP` remains a secondary incoming path alongside content URI triggers; see `App.onCreate()` / `registerReceiver` with `RECEIVER_EXPORTED` on API 33+.
- Prefer matching existing Java style (package `com.zegoggles.smssync`, Otto bus, preference keys in `Preferences`).
- When touching manifests, keep `android:exported` explicit on components with intent filters.
- Do not remove RCS/group addressing logic in mail conversion without review.
